description: Named for its freckled and blue eyed owners, Freckled & Blue, is serving up some delicious southern comfort foods with a gourmet twist. Their seasonal menu features great tasting dishes like their Tomato, Basil & Feta Orzo and their f.a.b Deviled Eggs. In addition you can rack up some good karma points for eating at this truck, because for every meal purchased from Freckled & Blue, they serve a community member in need.
name: Freckled & Blue
